<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>BoxLang AI Bootcamp / Bootcamp de BoxLang AI</title>
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>BoxLang AI Bootcamp</h1>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="jumbotron">
                    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to the BoxLang AI Bootcamp!</h1>
                    <p class="lead"> This is your starting point for learning how to use BoxLang to create amazing AI applications.</p>
                    <hr class="my-4">
                    
                    <p class="lead">
                      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/en/index.bxm" role="button">Get Started</a>
                    </p>
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="jumbotron">
                    <h1 class="display-4">Bienvenido al Bootcamp de BoxLang AI!</h1>
                    <p class="lead">Este es tu punto de partida para aprender a utilizar BoxLang para crear increíbles aplicaciones de AI.</p>
                    <hr class="my-4">
                    <p class="lead">
                      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/es/index.bxm" role="button">Empezar</a>
                    </p>
                  </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        

        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    </body>
</html>